chara.textHome:
It's me, Madoka-senpai,
star of the world of Magia Report.
Maybe you know me from Magia Record?

Iroha's bawling her eyes out 'cause she
can't pull anything good in the Fate Weave.
No, not THIS Iroha, my Iroha...
Yikes, this is getting confusing.

Anyways, I may be lacking a star,
but I'm the Magia Report star,
Madoka-senpai.
Good to see ya.

It's really hard to reason with me
when I'm in Madokannon mode.

Once I get amped up
I'm already showering down artillery,
so make sure to take shelter, 'kay?

So basically this means
my kicking strength increased, yeah?

Looks like they already put two of me
in the game.
The other me starts out as a ★4,

so I guess going from a ★3 to a ★4
is one of my unique traits...
And no, I am happy!

There's regular me and Kimono me,
and now my Magia Report self is
in the game too.

Soon you'll be able to form a team
that's just me.

Obviously you're gonna call on
Magia Report me as your support, right?
Thanks for your letter!
We'll fix your problems in a flash!
Huh? That's not why you're here?
Mornin'. Were you up late?
Playing too much Magia Record?
Oh, a different game...
I see...

So this is the Kamihama
from the Magia Record-verse...

Maybe it's got a ramen shop
that'll blow my mind?

Got any recommendations,
Magia Record Iroha?
Look at that star twinkling up there.

You know, I'm only a ★3 because
I gave a star to the sky.

Magia Record is fun, but be smart
and don't stay up all night playing!
...The items you need didn't drop yet?
Yeah, that happens...

I can hear Magia Report Iroha
bawling from here.

Guess she got her butt kicked by
that 1% rate again...
Having trouble with a quest?
Let a Support Character handle it!
Right, Iroha?
Oh, this paper? It's for Mirrors.

Huh? You Magia Record guys don't
decide your fights with paper football?

It's nice we got to meet
Homura by pre-registering.
Everyone can see her that way.

Hey, wait a sec?
Don't tell me you didn't pre-register?

This world's Mami joined some
weird cult too, huh?

The other version of me asked us
if we could help bring her back.

Kyoko says she plays Magia Record
on Mami's phone.

Seems like she installed
a ton of other games, too.

Sayaka... 
Oh, should we not talk about her yet?

I hope she gets added...
I mean, I hope we can meet her soon.
Huh? You can meet her already?!
I do this radio show with Iroha, and...
Whoa! Iroha, you look kinda different.
Maybe it's the way you're drawn?
Our next letter asks:
"Please tell me how to get a ★4"...
Ummm...well...

You know, there's a
★3 Madoka-senpai out there!

Drinking Himika's "Feral Juice" may be
grueling, but it kinda grows on you.

But what does Mitama use it for...
Let's not even think about it.
Woo hoo!
Magia Report Iroha, you seein' this?!
At last, I'm available in Magia Record!

Wow, I gotta say something special when
you're showing me this much love...
Wanna chat about cherry tomatoes?

Do you really think you stand a chance
against Lock-n-Load Madoka?
Ma! Gi! Repo! Did you all join in?
Ma! Gi! Reco! Did you all join in?
This is the true power of a senpai.
I'll bring this home as a souvenir.

S'up, this is Madoka-senpai coming at you
live from the world of Magia Report.

My dream is to see only myself
in the support list.
Good to see ya.
Oh, I leveled up!

Iroha, you seein' this?
I'm stronger than ever!
What are you asking me?

...Your name shouldn't be Iroha,
it should be LEER-oha!
I just met the Magia Record me...

Should I have done that though?
The world's not gonna implode, is it?
It's okay?

I took a trip to Hawaii for New Year's,
but I guess in this universe me and Homura
put on kimonos and went to a shrine.
